videos.description: Illinois' Giorgi Bezhanishvili chases down Jaedon LeDee on the break and completely shuts down his dunk attempt against the backboard.
videos.headline: Illinois' Bezhanishvili completely stuffs LeDee's dunk attempt

videos.description: Duane Washington Jr. jumps as high as he can to grab the lob pass and finishes strong at the rim with a layup through the defense.
videos.headline: Washington catches lob, finishes strong layup
